<meta name="SUMMARY"
content="JIMMY MONTGOMERY STILL IN PRISON: CONDITION DETERIORATING, AS GOVERNOR'S OFFICE DOES 'SPIN CONTROL'...ATLANTA MAYORS' PROHIBITIONIST SUMMIT A PROPAGANDA FAILURE! ENTERTAINMENT INDUSTRY LAUNCHES NEW 'ANTI-LEGALIZATION' EFFORT...NORML TO PRESENT LETTER TO DUTCH AMBASSADOR; JOINS INTERNATIONAL SUPPORT FOR DUTCH DRUG POLICY...SLAIN MARIJUANA USER'S FAMILY FILES WRONGFUL DEATH SUIT...CALIFORNIA IS 'BUZZING' WITH MEDICINAL MARIJUANA NEWS...">
