<HEAD><TITLE>The Crisis in Australian Public Broadcasting</TITLE></HEAD> 
<BODY BGCOLOR="#FFFFFF">

<table border=0 cellpadding=0 width=475><tr>
<IMG WIDTH=475 SRC="/../images/online.gif" ALT="The Online Journalist">
<IMG VSPACE=10 SRC="/../resources/dot_clear.gif"><BR>
<td width=20><BR></td><td ALIGN=center>
<H1>The Crisis in Australian Public Broadcasting</H1>
</td><td width=10><BR></td></tr></table>

<IMG height=2 width=468 SRC="/../resources/dot_peri.gif"><br>
<IMG vspace=5 hspace=0 SRC="/../resources/dot_clear.gif"><br>

<TABLE CELLSPACING=0 CELLPADDING=5 BORDER=0 WIDTH=475>
<TR><TD ALIGN=CENTER VALIGN=TOP COLSPAN=30>
<IMG vspace=2 hspace=0 SRC="/../resources/dot_clear.gif"><br>
<IMG width=30 SRC="/../images/tiny-logo-acij.gif"></TD>
<TD COLSPAN=10></TD>
<TD ALIGN=LEFT COLSPAN=350><FONT SIZE=+1>
<BR>
<A HREF="crisisreport.html"><H3>The Crisis in Australian Public Broadcasting</H3></A><BR>
Attacks on the ABC and SBS signal a crisis for the independence of Australia's public broadcasting system. The Australian Centre for Independent Journalism held a public seminar in August to discuss the situation. A report by Sumegha Agarwal.</FONT></TD></TR>
<TR><TD ALIGN=CENTER VALIGN=TOP COLSPAN=30>
<IMG vspace=2 hspace=0 SRC="/../resources/dot_clear.gif"><br>
<IMG width=30 SRC="/../images/tiny-logo-acij.gif"></TD>
<TD COLSPAN=10></TD>
<TD ALIGN=LEFT COLSPAN=350><FONT SIZE=+1>
<BR>
<A HREF="abcsubmission.html"><H3>Submission to the ABC Review</H3></A><BR>
The ABC Review, headed up by Bob Mansfield, called for public submissions. The Department for Social Communication and Journalism, University of Technology, Sydney and the Australian Centre For Independent Journalism submitted their concerns.</FONT></TD></TR>
<TR><TD ALIGN=CENTER VALIGN=TOP COLSPAN=30>
<IMG vspace=2 hspace=0 SRC="/../resources/dot_clear.gif"><br>
<IMG width=30 SRC="/../images/tiny-logo-acij.gif"></TD>
<TD COLSPAN=10></TD>
<TD ALIGN=LEFT COLSPAN=350><FONT SIZE=+1>
<BR>
<A HREF="ABC-Preamble.html"><H3>Public Service Broadcasting Research Group Submission</H3></A><BR>
The Public Service Broadcasting Research Group submission to the<BR>
ABC Review. </FONT></TD></TR>
<TR><TD ALIGN=CENTER VALIGN=TOP COLSPAN=30>
<IMG vspace=2 hspace=0 SRC="/../resources/dot_clear.gif"><br>
<IMG width=30 SRC="/../images/tiny-logo-acij.gif"></TD>
<TD COLSPAN=10></TD>
<TD ALIGN=LEFT COLSPAN=350><FONT SIZE=+1>
<BR>
<A HREF="cox-01.html"><H3>The Public  Broadcaster and Civil Society</H3></A><BR>
The Women's Economic Think Tank (WETTANK) submission to the<BR>
ABC Review. Prepared by Eva Cox.</FONT></TD></TR>
</TD></TR><TR>
</TABLE>
</FONT>

<IMG vspace=10 hspace=0 SRC="/../resources/dot_clear.gif"><br>
<IMG height=2 width=468 SRC="/../resources/dot_peri.gif"><br>
