<B>Uni Tavur</B> is the award-winning newspaper  published by students at the South Pacific Centre for Communication & Information in Development ( <A HREF="../UniTavur/UniT_SPCenCIID.html">SPCenCIID</A> ), at the University of Papua New Guinea.  <BR><BR>This Web edition has been developed as a joint project of SPCenCIID and the Australian Centre for Independent Journalism (<A HREF="index.html">ACIJ</A>), at the University of Technology, Sydney.
<p>
