<HTML> 
<HEAD><TITLE>ACIJ - "Making a Difference"</TITLE></HEAD> 
<BODY BGCOLOR="#FFFFFF">


<table border=0 cellpadding=0 width=475><tr>
<td width=230>
<IMG HEIGHT=100 ALIGN=LEFT SRC="/images/logo-acij.gif"> <center></td><td width=120><BR></td>
<td>
<Font size=6>
<B>MAKING A DIFFERENCE</font><BR><BR>
<Font size=5>
<B>A short film looking at how the media treats indigenous and ethnic affairs</font>
</td></center></tr></table>
<PRE></PRE>

<IMG VSPACE=10 SRC="/resources/dot_clear.gif"><BR>
<FONT SIZE=4>"Making a Difference" looks at how infotainment news values, like 'conflict', have dominated coverage of Aboriginal and ethnic issues in the Australian media. <p>The video gives a voice to those affected by negative coverage, and shows how perceptions of indigenous and ethnic people have been shaped. <p>The video concludes that by balancing traditional news values with empowering images, it is possible to make news positive. </font>
<BR><BR><BR><P>
<Font size=5>
<B>Watch a short clip from "Making a Difference".</font><BR>
<p><Font size=4>
This is a Quicktime format video clip. You can use <A HREF="http://quicktime.apple.com/">video playback programs</A> such as MoviePlayer, Simple Player or similar to view it. Two versions of the clip are provided - a high quality version and a medium quality version. Please note that the high quality clip is 2.5MB and takes ages to download; the medium quality clip is a slimmer 1.4MB and still takes a while - plenty of time to go and make that nice cup of tea you've been promising yourself.<p>
<b><A HREF="/ACIJ/videohi.mov">"Making a Difference"</A></b> video clip - High quality: 2.5MB<BR><BR>
<b><A HREF="/ACIJ/videomed.mov">"Making a Difference"</A></b> video clip - Medium quality: 1.4MB</font>
<BR><BR><Font size=4><B>Note:</B> If you have any feedback about the video clip, please send comments to me: <A HREF="mailto:p.cronau@uts.edu.au"> Peter Cronau</A>, Web Editor.</Font><BR><BR><BR>
<Font size=5>
<B>You can order a copy of the "Making a Difference" video.</font><BR>
<p><Font size=4>
An 18 minute documentary suitable for an interested audience and educational institutions. The order form is located on the <b><A HREF="/ACIJ/resources.html">ACIJ Resources</A> </b> page.</font>
<p>
<IMG VSPACE=4 SRC="/resources/dot_clear.gif"><BR>

<table border=0 cellspacing=0 cellpadding=0 width=450><tr><td>
<A HREF="/index.html"><IMG alt=return to ACIJ Homepage BORDER=0 ALIGN=BASELINE WIDTH=25 HEIGHT=27 SRC="/images/tiny-logo-acij.gif">Return to ACIJ homepage</A>
</td></tr></table>

</BODY> 
</HTML> 
