    <DT><H3 ADD_DATE="815015336">
<A NAME="publications">PUBLICATIONS</A></H3>
    <DL><p>
        
        <DT><A HREF="http://www.smh.com.au/">The Sydney Morning Herald</A>
        <DT><A HREF="http://www.theage.com.au/">The Age</A>
<DT><A HREF="http://www.mediainfo.com/edpub/index.html" >Editor & Publisher Home Page</A>
