<Font size=7>Centre for Communication and Information in Development </CENTER></A></Font size=7>
<HR>
<P>
<CENTER><A HREF="http://www.eff.org/blueribbon.html"><IMG SRC="spcenciid/images/freespeech.gif"></A><BR></CENTER>
<P><table border=0 cellpadding=0 width=100%><tr><td>
<P>
<IMG SRC="spcenciid/images/bullet.gif">The South Pacific Centre for Communication and Information in Development (SPCenCIID) of the University of Papua New Guinea has taken on a pioneering role in development communication and research in the region. It combines the resources of journalism, library and information studies. It produces a range of publications and resources.</td></tr></table>
