<BODY BGCOLOR="#FFFFFF">
<TITLE>Media Magazine</TITLE>
<A NAME="top"></A>
<CENTER>
<IMG WIDTH=350 ALIGN=CENTRE HEIGHT=218 SRC="images/mm.title.jpg">
<BR>

<IMG WIDTH=450 ALIGN=CENTRE HEIGHT=50 SRC="images/banner.home.jpg">
</CENTER>
<BR>
<BR>
<FONT SIZE=4><I>Media Magazine</I>  is Australia's national community radio program on media and communications - providing independent, incisive and accessible analysis.  You can listen to <I>Media Magazine</I> on more than twenty community radio stations around Australia or buy cassette tapes of recent programs.   For media and communications specialists, students or the interested punter - you should find plenty to chew on here.
<BR><BR><BR>
<CENTER>
<H2><BLINK><B>Stop Press</B></BLINK></H2>
</CENTER>
<BR>
<UL>
<H3>

<LI>Summer programming details are <a href="./summer/index.html">here</a>.  Summer programming - features and documentaries from 1996 will continue until early February
<BR><BR>
<LI>In December 1996 <I>Media Magazine</I> won a high commendation in the category of regularly broadcast spoken word program at the 1996 CBAA Annual Awards.
<BR><BR>
<LI>The Community Broadcasting Foundation has renewed its financial support of <I>Media Magazine</I> at an increased level in 1997.  Thanks to the CBF and our other major supporter, the Australian Film Commission.</H3>
</UL>
<BR>
<BR>
<CENTER>
<A HREF="./about/index.html"><IMG BORDER=0 WIDTH=142 ALIGN=CENTRE HEIGHT=57 SRC="images/button.flat.blob.intro.jpg"></a>
<A HREF="./1996programs/index.html"><IMG BORDER=0 WIDTH=142 ALIGN=CENTRE HEIGHT=57 SRC="images/button.flat.blob.program.jpg"></a>
<A HREF="./broadcast/index.html"><IMG BORDER=0 WIDTH=142 ALIGN=CENTRE HEIGHT=57 SRC="images/button.flat.blob.broadcast.jpg"></a>
<A HREF="./sponsors/index.html"><IMG BORDER=0 WIDTH=142 ALIGN=CENTRE HEIGHT=57 SRC="images/button.flat.blob.sponsors.jpg"></a>
<A HREF="./buy/index.html"><IMG BORDER=0 WIDTH=142 ALIGN=CENTRE HEIGHT=57 SRC="images/button.flat.blob.buy.jpg"></a>
<A HREF="./history/index.html"><IMG BORDER=0 WIDTH=142 ALIGN=CENTRE HEIGHT=57 SRC="images/button.flat.blob.history.jpg"></a>
<BR>
<BR>
<BR>
<BR>

<IMG WIDTH=236 HEIGHT=157 ALIGN=CENTRE SRC="images/mm.australia.6.gif" >
<BR>
<BR>
<BR>
<A HREF="http://www.bscene.com.au/2ser"><IMG BORDER=0 WIDTH=142 ALIGN=CENTRE HEIGHT=57 SRC="images/button.flat.blob.2ser.jpg"></a>
<A HREF="./commedia/index.html"><IMG BORDER=0 WIDTH=170 ALIGN=CENTRE HEIGHT=57 SRC="images/button.flat.blob.commedia.jpg"></a>
<A HREF="./ausmedia/index.html"><IMG BORDER=0 WIDTH=220 ALIGN=CENTRE HEIGHT=57 SRC="images/button.flat.blob.ausmedia.jpg"></a>
</CENTER>
<BR>
<BR>
Media and communications are playing an ever increasing role in our lives.  More than ever we need to take a critical approach to media and communications policy and practice.  This site has new information each week - so make <I>Media Magazine</I> part of your routine.
<BR>
