</CENTER>
</td></tr></table>

<IMG vspace=5 hspace=0 SRC="/../resources/dot_clear.gif"><br>
<IMG height=2 width=485 SRC="/../resources/dot_peri.gif"><br>
<IMG vspace=5 hspace=0 SRC="/../resources/dot_clear.gif"><br>

<table border=0 cellspacing=0 cellpadding=0 width=475><tr>
<td width=40><BR></td>
<td width=430><FONT SIZE=+1>
<B>The following message was received on September 24 in response to protests to the Tongan government by Pacific Journalism Review and the Australian Centre for Independent Journalism:</B>
<BR><IMG VSPACE=6 SRC="/../resources/dot_clear.gif"><BR>
On behalf of the editor, Kalafi Moala, subeditor Filokalafi 'Akau'ola, and the staff of the Taimi 'o Tonga newspaper, I would like to convey to you our sincere thanks for the support that you, and the various media organisations affiliated, have made in the attempt to release the two journalists who are imprisoned up to this moment, including Member of Parliament 'Akilisi Pohiva.
<BR><IMG VSPACE=6 SRC="/../resources/dot_clear.gif"><BR>
We are very happy to understand that there are people somewhere who are willing to stand up to protect our rights to disseminate information and attempt to sustain and restore freedom of speech and of the press, not only throughout the region, but in this tiny kingdom. 
<BR><IMG VSPACE=6 SRC="/../resources/dot_clear.gif"><BR>
Kalafi Moala and Filokalafi 'Akau'ola have been shifted yesterday to the main prison, Hu'atolitoli, while Pohiva, due to his illness, is being treated at the Vaiola Hospital.
<BR><IMG VSPACE=6 SRC="/../resources/dot_clear.gif"><BR>
While in hospital there is a police officer there to make sure that only his immediate family and people who come to pray together with him visits. 
<BR><IMG VSPACE=6 SRC="/../resources/dot_clear.gif"><BR>
Pohiva may return to jail after he recovers. 
<BR><IMG VSPACE=6 SRC="/../resources/dot_clear.gif"><BR>
At the moment it is only the Parliament [which] can make the decision to decline the penalty or decrease the number of days imposed on the three to be imprisoned.
<BR><IMG VSPACE=6 SRC="/../resources/dot_clear.gif"><BR>
We are facing difficulty at the moment with only two reporters and not only that but we have yet to be granted any opportunity to visit our editor and his assistant for further advice regarding the operation of the newspaper. 
<BR><IMG VSPACE=6 SRC="/../resources/dot_clear.gif"><BR>
<B>Yours,
<BR><IMG VSPACE=6 SRC="/../resources/dot_clear.gif"><BR>
Siosiua P. Pohiva</B>
</FONT>
</td></tr></table>

<IMG vspace=5 hspace=0 SRC="/../resources/dot_clear.gif"><br>
<IMG height=2 width=485 SRC="/../resources/dot_peri.gif"><br>
<IMG vspace=5 hspace=0 SRC="/../resources/dot_clear.gif"><br>

