<table border=0 cellspacing=0 cellpadding=0 width=475><tr>
<td width=70><BR></td>
<td width=370>
<B>RSF PROTEST TO THE KING OF TONGA</B>
<BR><IMG VSPACE=6 SRC="/../resources/dot_clear.gif"><BR>
<B>Your Excellency,</B>
<BR><IMG VSPACE=6 SRC="/../resources/dot_clear.gif"><BR>
Reporters Sans Frontieres, an independent organisation working to defend press freedom worldwide, wishes to strongly protest against the imprisonment of newspaper editors.
<BR><IMG VSPACE=6 SRC="/../resources/dot_clear.gif"><BR>
According to our information, Filokalafi 'Akau'ola, deputy editor of the Tongan weekly Taimi O Tonga , and the Auckland based editor Kalafi Moala have each been sentenced to one month in jail for contempt of parliament. 
<BR><IMG VSPACE=6 SRC="/../resources/dot_clear.gif"><BR>
On 23 February 1996, Filokalafi 'Akau'ola had already been arrested and detained following the publication of letters concerning Minister of Police Clive Edwards. He was kept in custody for 26 hours before being released on bail and ordered to appear in te Magistrates' Court on Wednesday 26 February to face criminal charges that he had threatened a civil servant, under section 57 of the Tongan criminal code. 
<BR><IMG VSPACE=6 SRC="/../resources/dot_clear.gif"><BR>
The police had also raided the newspaper office in search of the original copy of the offending letter.
<BR><IMG VSPACE=6 SRC="/../resources/dot_clear.gif"><BR>
We protest against the imprisonment of Filokalafi 'Akau'ola and Kalafi Moala as a direct attack on press freedom and as a disproportionate sentence. Press freedom and freedom of expression are to be respected, and we request the release of these two journlists and ask you to do everything in your power to ensure that press freedom is allowed to exist in Tonga.
<BR><IMG VSPACE=6 SRC="/../resources/dot_clear.gif"><BR>
We thank you for your attention and would welcome your comments. 
<BR><IMG VSPACE=10 SRC="/../resources/dot_clear.gif"><BR>
Sincerely,<BR>
Robert Menard<BR>
General Secretary<BR>
20th September, 1996<BR>
<BR><IMG VSPACE=6 SRC="/../resources/dot_clear.gif"><BR>
<B>REPORTERS SANS FRONTIERES<BR>
Secretariat International<BR>
5, rue Geoffroy Marie 75009 Paris - France<BR> 
Tel: (33) 1 44 83 84 84<BR>
Fax: (33) 1 45 23 11 51<BR>
Email <A HREF="MAILTO:rsf@calvacom.calvanet.fr">rsf@calvacom.calvanet.fr</A></B>
</td>
<td width=30></td>
</tr></table>

