<B></B><HTML> 
<HEAD><TITLE>JAILING OF TONGAN JOURNALISTS</TITLE></HEAD> 
<BODY BGCOLOR="#FFFFFF">
 
<table border=0 cellpadding=0 width=475><tr>
<A NAME="top"><IMG WIDTH=475 SRC="/../images/online.gif" ALT="The Online Journalist"></A>
<IMG VSPACE=10 SRC="/../resources/dot_clear.gif"><BR>
<td width=20><BR></td><td ALIGN=center>
<H1>Pacific Concerns Resource Centre, Fiji, response</H1>
</td><td width=10><BR></td>
</tr></table>

<IMG height=2 width=485 SRC="/../resources/dot_peri.gif"><br>
<IMG vspace=5 hspace=0 SRC="/../resources/dot_clear.gif"><br>

<table border=0 cellspacing=0 cellpadding=0 width=475><tr>
<td width=20><BR></td>
<td width=450>
<CENTER>
<A HREF="tonga-free.html"><B>[Tongan Journalists Free!]</B></A><BR>
<A HREF="tonga.html">[Jailing of Tongan Journalists]</A>  
<A HREF="tonga-ACIJ.html">[ACIJ condemns attack]</A>  
<A HREF="tonga-PJR.html">[PJR protests]</A>  
<A HREF="tonga-IFEX.html">[IFEX response]</A><BR>  
<A HREF="tonga-IFJ.html">[IFJ response]</A>  
<A HREF="tonga-Times.html">[Message from Tonga Times]</A>  <A HREF="tonga-Gov.html">[Response from the Tongan Government]</A><BR> 
<A HREF="tonga-RSF.html">[RSF response]</A>  
<A HREF="tonga-terrorism.html">['Media terrorism']</A>  
[PCRC, Fiji, response]
<A HREF="tonga-PFIN.html">[PFIN response]</A><BR>
<A HREF="tonga-PINA.html">[PINA appeal to king]</A>  
<A HREF="tonga-chronicle.html">[Tongan Chronicle report]</A>  
<A HREF="tonga-otherweb.html">[Other Web sources of information]</A><BR>
<A HREF="tonga-what.html">[What you can do]</A>
</CENTER>
</td></tr></table>

<IMG vspace=5 hspace=0 SRC="/../resources/dot_clear.gif"><br>
<IMG height=2 width=485 SRC="/../resources/dot_peri.gif"><br>
<IMG vspace=5 hspace=0 SRC="/../resources/dot_clear.gif"><br>

<table border=0 cellspacing=0 cellpadding=0 width=475><tr>
<td width=70><BR></td>
<td width=370>
<B>PCRC letter to Tongan Prime Minister</B>
<BR><IMG VSPACE=6 SRC="/../resources/dot_clear.gif"><BR>
<B>Your Excellency,</B>
<BR><IMG VSPACE=6 SRC="/../resources/dot_clear.gif"><BR>
Please accept our peaceful greetings and best wishes. 
<BR><IMG VSPACE=6 SRC="/../resources/dot_clear.gif"><BR>
Please also accept our humble apologies for this unsolicited intrusion but our collective conscience prompts us to convey to Your Excellency our great concern about the jailing of Kalafi Moala, Filokalafi Akau'ola and Akilisi Pohiva. 
<BR><IMG VSPACE=6 SRC="/../resources/dot_clear.gif"><BR>
We do not question the existence of the Kingdom's legislation relating to contempt of Parliament nor do we challenge the right of His Majesty's Government and Parliament to enact and execute such legislation. 
<BR><IMG VSPACE=6 SRC="/../resources/dot_clear.gif"><BR>
However we humbly proffer the view that the letter and spirit of such legislation is in violation of the universal right to freedom of expression and opinion which is entrenched in the Kingdom's Constitution. As such the Kingdom's contempt of Parliament legislation is unjust and oppressive. As a consequence the jailing of the three men is unjust and oppressive.
<BR><IMG VSPACE=6 SRC="/../resources/dot_clear.gif"><BR>
We therefore beseech Your Excellency that it is in the interests of His Majesty's Kingdom and Government for your Excellency to initiate proceedings in Parliament to ensure the immediate release of the 3 men and the eventual annulment of the Kingdom's contempt of Parliament legislation. 
<BR><IMG VSPACE=6 SRC="/../resources/dot_clear.gif"><BR>
Sir we humbly beg leave and again apologise for this intrusion. 
<BR><IMG VSPACE=10 SRC="/../resources/dot_clear.gif"><BR>
<B>Yours in Peace<BR>
Lopeti Senituli<BR>
Director<BR>
PCRC INC.<BR>
26 September 1996</B>
</td>
<td width=30></td>
</tr></table>

