<DOCHDR>
http://acij.uts.edu.au:80/pmw/docs/damocles.html 138.25.138.98 19970110074233 text/html 9622
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
MIME-Version: 1.0
Server: MacHTTP/2.2
Message-ID: <aefc3e15.301@138.25.138.98>
