<TD ALIGN=CENTER COLSPAN=2><P><B><FONT SIZE=+1>Next Story<BR><A HREF="indones.htm"><I>Indonesia's Big Bang</A></I></FONT></B><BR>
</TD></TR>

<TR><TD> </TD></TR>
