<HEAD><TITLE>Snoop: Selling Telstra - are we being dudded?</TITLE></HEAD>
  
<BODY BACKGROUND="../IMAGES/bgyellow.gif" TEXT="#000000" LINK="#0000ff">
<BASEFONT SIZE=3>

