<DOCHDR>
http://acij.uts.edu.au:80/cafepacific/resources/aspac/cyber.html 138.25.138.98 19970110095644 text/html 12354
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
MIME-Version: 1.0
Server: MacHTTP/2.2
Message-ID: <aefc5d83.585@138.25.138.98>
