<center>
<h1>East Timor Images 1942 - 1996</h1>
<img src="../images/colorbar.gif"></p><br><br><br><br>
<img src="photos/womsoldier.jpg"></p><br>
Timorese women played an active part in the resistance.  In addition to food gathering and child rearing, women were involved in the defence of East Timorese controlled territory.  Shown here a group makes its way along a stream in wet season.</p>
Smuggled photo (photographer unknown) - circa 1977</p><br>
<img src="../images/colorbar.gif"><br><br><br>
