<LI><A HREF="intersections/index.html">INTERSECTIONS WITH ASIA:</A></B> The future of international journalism.
This conference, held in Sydney on November 11th and 12th, 1996 looks at Asia and the Pacific - the fastest growing media markets in the world. Conference proceedings are being placed online as they become available.
<LI><B><A HREF="ACIJ/Crisis/crisis.html">The Crisis in Australian Public Broadcasting</A></B>  The budgetary and ideological attacks on public broadcasting in Australia. Includes ACIJ submission to the current review.
