</UL><LI><Strong>UPNG students back off strike.  </strong>( Reporters : Joseph Morokana )
<UL><LI>Students meeting at an urgent forum yesterday to debate the fees issue decided to petition the Government to reinstate the  National Scholarship system.
</UL><LI><Strong>Communications overhaul for university bill tops K300,000. </strong> ( Reporter : Christine Banian )
